main event: A civilian observer photographed a UFO phenomenon consisting of multiple bright lights over Ventnor, New Jersey on 20 December 1967.
interesting points: The observer reported seeing a block of lights appearing circular in shape,The observation was made during a six second exposure of the stars,Insufficient data was provided for a full evaluation as original negatives were not received,The sighting was made while standing in front of the observer's home at night,The observer noted that the lights were glowing brightly and illuminated the area.
sighted object: multiple bright lights in a circular formation
